FBIS4-12563 "drnes069_k_94002" FBIS-NES-94-069 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 IRAQ Turkish `Warplanes' Reportedly Attack Kurd Villages Turkish `Warplanes' Reportedly Attack Kurd Villages NC0604172094 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1605 GMT 6 Apr 94 NC0604172094 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1605 GMT 6 Apr 94 Arabic BFN [Excerpts] The day before yesterday a squadron of Turkish warplanes attacked several villages and hamlets inside the Kurdistan region on the pretext that Kurdish Workers Party [PKK] elements are in the area, which is near the Turkish border. [passage omitted] The attacks caused no civilian casualties.
